  attackDescription: "Fast precision strikes that deal high damage if the enemy is
    caught off\u2011guard."
  defenseDescription: "Relies on agility rather than toughness \u2014 can dodge hits
    but doesn\u2019t withstand many direct blows."
  speedDescription: "Extremely fast movement and attack speed, excels at repositioning
    and hit\u2011and\u2011run tactics."
  ultimateDescription: "Shadow Courier \u2014 a sudden burst of speed followed by
    multiple invisible strikes delivered in a blink."
  story: "A silent master of movement and deception, the Ninja trained in hidden
    mountain temples where combat is treated as an art. He carries no weapons \u2014
    his body is the blade. His ultimate, Shadow Courier, is a technique so fast that
    enemies swear they were struck by a dozen blows at once."
  shortDescription: "A lightning\u2011fast unarmed assassin who relies on agility
    and precision, finishing enemies with the Shadow Courier technique."
